###################################################################################################################
#                                                                                                                 #
# This is a github repo of my Sysadmin detection scripts.                                                         #
#                                                                                                                 #
# This task is about analyzing what commands the users of an IT system use during their work. The main question   #
# to investigate is whether it is possible to distinguish between users based on their usage of commands.         #
#                                                                                                                 #
# These were written on Ubuntu 16.04 64bit OS using R v3.4 with h2o v3.10.4.5, JavaRE (build 1.8.0_131-b11)       #
# and BASH scripts.                                                                                               #
# Dependent tools should be installed prior to usage:                                                             #
#    ~$ sudo apt-get update                                                                                       #
#    ~$ sudo apt-get install mawk sed coreutils python-pip r-base                                                 #
#    ~$ sudo pip install csvkit                                                                                   #
#                                                                                                                 #
#                                                                                                                 #
# usage:                                                                                                          #
# -td={path/to/training_files}                                                                                    #
# -tsd={path/to/public_test.csv}                                                                                  #
# -wd={path/to/intermediary/and/result/files}                                                                     #
#                                                                                                                 #
# 	~$ ./Sysadmin_detection_script -td=./_ds_task/training_files/ -tsd=./_ds_task/ -wd=./                         #
#                                                                                                                 #
###################################################################################################################

